text: Natalya "Natasha" Zvereva (; born April 16, 1971) is a retired tennis player from Belarus. Playing initially for the Soviet Union, Zvereva won many doubles titles during the late 1980s and throughout the 1990s. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1971 births Category:Belarusian tennis players Category:Female tennis players Category:French Open champions Category:Living people Category:Medalists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:US Open (tennis) champions Category:Wimbledon champions
title: Natasha Zvereva
